Infosys _FoodTrends Understanding Customer Preferences in FB - Group 1

* Name: D A Ajay
* Role: Data Visualization Intern at Infosys
* Tool Used: Power BI

📖 Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing food consumption patterns, nutrient impacts, and lifestyle influences using interactive dashboards. Each milestone highlights key insights derived from data to support better decision-making in the food and beverage domain.
Worked on 4 MILESTONE'S:


🔹 Milestone 1: Dietary Preferences and Averages
Analyzed user dietary patterns
Identified average consumption trends
Visualized category-wise food preferences

![Dashboard 1](./milestone-1.png)  >>Preview

dataset link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/adilshamim8/daily-food-and-nutrition-dataset

🔹 Milestone 2: Nutrients and Diseases
Explored relationships between nutrients and diseases
Highlighted key risk factors
Built comparative visual reports

![Dashboard 2](./milestone-2.png)  >>Preview

dataset link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/adilshamim8/daily-food-and-nutrition-dataset

🔹 Milestone 3: Averages by Breakfast Suggestion
Generated breakfast recommendations based on averages
Created visual insights for healthier choices


![Dashboard 3](./milestone-3.png)  >>Preview

dataset link: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ziya07/diet-recommendations-dataset

🔹 Milestone 4: Lifestyle and Nutrition Impact
Studied how lifestyle factors affect nutrition
Built correlation dashboards between habits and health outcomes

![Dashboard 4](./milestone-4.png)  >>Preview

datset link: https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/download-datasets


